I was SO happy you said the rooms might be TOO COLD!!!

I wanted to wear a dress that has long sleeves. Well, I wasn't even going to
bring it, but now I think I will.

This summer has been the hottest on record in New Mexico (July was, anyway)
and I would LOVE to be in a severely air conditioned place for a while.

Sandra
